dc_title_s: Political, commercial, and historical sketch maps of the British Empire: designed to illustrate Mr. G. R. parkin's address on "The geographical unity of the British empire".
dc_description_s: 5 maps: col.; on sheet 39 x 49 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
